  "texts": [
    "The efficiency of the hyperbolic scheme including the stabilization effect of the saturation factor in MAN-CHA3D code have recently been studied in (Navarro et al., 2022).",
    "The system of Eqs.",
    "1 -4 contains the Ohmic and ambipolar diffusion terms, Hall term, and Biermann battery term, with coefficients calculated as η = α e (en e) 2;",
    "Here, ξ n = ρ n /ρ is the fraction of neutrals, ρ n the neutral mass density, and e the electron charge.",
    "The neutral and electron collisional parameters, α n and α e, are defined as"
  ]
}